Reasoning: The paper deals with analyzing the effect of wording on message propagation on Twitter, which involves natural language processing and social network analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper also involves analyzing the language used in tweets, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves statistical analysis and experimentation, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper also involves predicting the popularity of tweets, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
